    ProductLatticeOntologySolverDisplayActions

    protected static class ProductLatticeOntologySolverDisplayActions.ProductLatticeHighlighterController
extends OntologyDisplayActions.HighlighterController
    The controller that adds commands to the context menu. This extends the HighlighterController in OntologyDisplayActions by adding a submenu to select which of the component ontologies in the product lattice ontology to use as a basis for highlighting the resolved concepts.
